STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Kendenson SAUVEUR, Defendant-Petitioner. C-940 September Term 2018
082244 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000608-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
